Package island

Class Animal

java.lang.Object
island.Animal
Direct Known Subclasses:
Cat, Grub, Kiwi, Rabbit, Rat, Sparrow
public abstract class Animal extends Object
The Animal class models the animal on the island. It provides methods for: - move towards food(abstract) - move towards water(abstract) - move towards partner(abstract) - eat - drink
Author:
Meiqiao
